=== ENTERTAINMENT_SYSTEM ===
# id: 95
# title: The Entertainment System
# chinese_title: 娱乐系统
# category: Terminal
# mode: dungeon

A recreational terminal offers a library of games, music, and educational programs. Among them, you find a language-learning program for Chinese characters that uses radical decomposition. The program's AI tutor springs to life, eager for a new student after years of dormancy.

* [Complete a lesson with the AI tutor]
  ~ gain_radical("禾")
  "禾" (hé) — grain, cereal crop. A fundamental radical in many characters.
* [Play a vocabulary-building game]
  ~ gain_xp(25)
  "玩" (wán) — to play, to have fun
* [Download the educational program]
  ~ gain_item("neural_boost")
  "习" (xí) — to practice, to learn
* [Listen to the music library instead]
  ~ heal(10)
  "乐" (lè) — joy, music, happiness
